ZH: 这个字怎么写？
EN: How do you write this character?
ZH: 我的中文名字有三个字。
EN: My Chinese name has three characters.
ZH: 你能认出这个字吗？
EN: Can you recognize this character?
ZH: 这个字的意思是什么？
EN: What does this character mean?
ZH: 请你写下这个字的汉字拼音。
EN: Please write the pinyin for this character.
ZH: 这篇文章里有很多难懂的字。
EN: There are many difficult characters in this article.
ZH: 我已经背下了一百个字。
EN: I have memorized one hundred characters already.
ZH: 这是一个常用的汉字。
EN: This is a commonly used Chinese character.
ZH: 我每天要练习写新的字。
EN: I have to practice writing new characters every day.
ZH: 这是我的筆名，是个特别的字。
EN: This is my pen name, it's a special character.
ZH: 他的中文名字只有两个字。
EN: His Chinese name only has two characters.
ZH: 我特别喜欢这个字的笔画。
EN: I really like the strokes of this character.
ZH: 我们的姓氏是一个很常见的字。
EN: Our surname is a very common character.
ZH: 这个字有多少种写法？
EN: How many different ways are there to write this character?
ZH: 我们要在作文里用这个字。
EN: We have to use this character in our composition.
ZH: 这个字是我最喜欢的汉字之一。
EN: This character is one of my favorite Chinese characters.
ZH: 我在字典里查到了这个字的意思。
EN: I found the meaning of this character in the dictionary.
ZH: 你认识这个字吗？它是很有意思的一个字。
EN: Do you know this character? It's a very interesting one.
ZH: 我们每周要学习五个新的字。
EN: We have to learn five new characters every week.
